ogether. His obligatory\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7655,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/cursing-killing-muslim-kufr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36990,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Muslims: Cursing him is wicked, killing is unbelief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDisparaging a Muslim is an act of wickedness, and fighting him is an act of unbelief.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7076, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 64 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/22\/punished-in-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":36990,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Punishment: Believers punished in world, sinners in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mughaffal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah wills to bless a servant, He hastens the punishment for his sins. If Allah wills to harm a servant, He withholds the punishment for his sins until he is brought forth on the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17467,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/04\/judge-deeds-not-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":36990,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Judgment: We judge outward deeds, not inner-states","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 4, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn 'Utbah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, people were judged by revelation in the time of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and the revelation has ceased. We only judge now what is manifested outwardly of your deeds.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14667,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/false-oaths-suicide-cursing-takfir\/","url_meta":{"origin":36990,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sins: False oaths, suicide, cursing, excommunication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Thabit ibn al-Dahhak reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever swears falsely by a religion other than Islam, he is what he has professed. Whoever kills himself with something, he will be punished with it in the fire of Hell. Cursing a believer is like killing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11210,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/08\/ibn-umar-kharijites-ayat-takfir\/","url_meta":{"origin":36990,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Umar on Rebels: Khawarij apply verses about unbelievers on Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, considered the Khawarij rebels to be the worst of Allah\u2019s creation and he said, \u201cIndeed, they take verses that were revealed about unbelievers and use them against believers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6531 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36990","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=36990"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36990\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-js